  "body": "On master (4f8b1f8759301d2553183e14f72444a0f1d80725) build tools for native packages are set to [defaults](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/ee7e06156357c333caef381b6acb3109d0187666/depends/builders/default.mk#L1-L8), even when such a tool is not available in the system by its default name:\r\n```\r\n$ make --no-print-directory -C depends print-native_b2_cxx CC=clang CXX=clang++\r\nnative_b2_cxx=g++\r\n$ make --no-print-directory -C depends print-native_capnp_cxx MULTIPROCESS=1 CC=clang CXX=clang++\r\nnative_capnp_cxx=g++\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe resulted problems are:\r\n```\r\n$ make --no-print-directory -C depends native_b2 CC=clang CXX=clang++\r\nBuilding native_b2...\r\nB2_TOOLSET is gcc, but the 'gcc' command cannot be executed.\r\nMake sure 'gcc' is in PATH, or use a different toolset.\r\nmake: *** [funcs.mk:281: /home/hebasto/GitHub/bitcoin/depends/work/build/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu/native_b2/1_71_0-793eacf1f74/tools/build/src/engine/.stamp_built] Error 1\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes this issue by introducing support of `{CC,CXX}_FOR_BUILD` variables.\r\n\r\nWith this PR:\r\n```\r\n$ make --no-print-directory -C depends print-native_b2_cxx CC_FOR_BUILD=clang CXX_FOR_BUILD=clang++\r\nnative_b2_cxx=clang++\r\n$ make --no-print-directory -C depends print-native_capnp_cxx MULTIPROCESS=1 CC_FOR_BUILD=clang CXX_FOR_BUILD=clang++\r\nnative_capnp_cxx=clang++\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis PR is an alternative to bitcoin/bitcoin#23551, and it is a more general solution.",
